PERMITTED USES (with valid license):
- Use of the Software on the licensed machine
- Integration into products and services per the license terms
- Access to all features enabled by the license tier

PROHIBITED USES (without valid license):
- Use of the Software beyond the free tier
- Redistribution, sublicensing, or resale
- Reverse engineering, decompilation, or disassembly
- Circumvention of hardware binding or license validation
